          <sel>isolationUpperOffsets:</sel>
          <arg type="NSData*">isolationUpperOffsets</arg>
          <desc>
            (M74) Designated initializer. The four trailing
            `NSData *` arguments must all be <code>nil</code>
            (legacy file) or all non-nil (M74 columns present —
            writer emits them when the
            `opt_ms2_activation_detail`
            flag is set by the author). Mixed nil/non-nil is
            rejected.
          </desc>
        </method>
